{"tid":713290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★游蕙禎入獄前拍片 「入獄既然不能避免，就當作係一種磨練。」","createTime":"2018-06-22T16:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T14:20:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":47,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cbc22b33407c7fd98c066f9624d462da78e74fc0","tid":713290,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"青年新政游蕙禎及梁頌恆在前年11月立法會宣誓風波中被控非法集結罪，游放棄上訴即時入獄4星期，估計在7月1日左右可以出獄。青年新政今日(22日)在社交網站上載一條游蕙禎在入獄前拍下的短片，死撐「入獄既然不能避免，就當作係一種磨練。」<br />\n<br />\n游在片段開首表示，「相信大家見到呢條片嘅時候代表我已經入獄」，她相信今次遭遇不是單一事件，並非開始，亦非結束。她指近年有不少人因為政治事件而被判入獄，可能會「覺得好氣餒，諗緊點解大家要堅持落去」，但她堅信終點不會一朝一夕到達，有好多人仍然為這個地方付出，希望大家積極參與抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n對於入獄，她說當作是磨練，希望自己不會停滯不前，出獄後能令自己更加強大，能趕上大家的步伐。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/photo/bkn-20180622231953532-0622_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180623002543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180622%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180622231953532-0622_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180623002543&d=gPG8u%2BcTOjN0AfjFGLeD0y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=c17f359a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/photo/bkn-20180622231953532-0622_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180623002543</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/bkn-20180622231953532-0622_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180622%2Fbkn-20180622231953532-0622_00822_001.html&d=gPG8u%2BcTOjN0AfjFGLeD0y7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=1606f7d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180622/bkn-20180622231953532-0622_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a05116801e40feb8616a46a0f1c878d8facf1637","tid":713290,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"886050526c3c2a5a125359f1711405e015269cc7","tid":713290,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"s